1
00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:01,210
Are you okay?

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:03,500
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:04,880
If I had shown up there,

4
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:06,130
you would've just given people

5
00:00:06,170 --> 00:00:08,040
something else to gossip about.

6
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,710
I asked your friend
to create a diversion.

7
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:13,500
This is so thrilling.

8
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:15,710
It's like we're playing hide-and-seek.

9
00:00:16,580 --> 00:00:17,580
And...

10
00:00:18,290 --> 00:00:18,580
our hands...

11
00:00:19,250 --> 00:00:20,250
are still intertwined.

12
00:00:22,130 --> 00:00:23,130
How cute.

13
00:00:23,540 --> 00:00:24,540
Sami.

14
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:26,170
How do you know
my name?

15
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:27,460
Take a guess.

16
00:00:28,420 --> 00:00:30,750
Why... are you helping me?

17
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:32,830
Because I find you interesting.

18
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,250
What is that...

19
00:00:35,380 --> 00:00:36,380
supposed to mean?

20
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,380
I hope you'll figure it out.

21
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:43,580
No.

22
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:44,790
I'm not letting you get away now.

23
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:47,880
Just hide in here for now.

24
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:49,710
I'll stay with you.

25
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:52,290
I have absolutely no idea
what this guy is thinking.

26
00:00:52,330 --> 00:00:52,670
Oh.

27
00:00:53,330 --> 00:00:54,330
Right.

28
00:00:57,960 --> 00:01:00,540
Ta-da!
I like this one too.

29
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,000
But there's one thing
I know for sure.

30
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,710
Which toy do you want?

31
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:06,580
Me?

32
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:09,000
I've always wanted
the toy ring.

33
00:01:09,380 --> 00:01:11,130
But I can never seem to get it.

34
00:01:11,710 --> 00:01:13,710
I really don't like this guy.
